    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--text-heading);
}

.editor-quote {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.65rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--editor-accent);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--editor-accent) 5%, transparent);
    color: var(--editor-text);
    font-style: italic;
}
```

#### Editor Content Styling
